name: MedicationProductForm
title: Medication Product Form
publisher: HL7 US Realm Program Management Steward
description: CCDA v2.1 definition appears to say all the descendents of C42636 that includes  many navigational concepts and even null-types. Not clear what the intended list should be. This is different than the SPL list by FDA 2.16.840.1.113883.3.26.1.1.2  which are all the concepts linked to "Structured Product Labeling Pharmaceutical Dosage Form Terminology (Code C54456)" by Concept_In_Subset (164 concepts as of 2016-08-02)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This is the physical form of the medicinal product as presented to the individual. This value set is defined by the US Federal Drug Administration.),(Data Element Scope: Medicinal drug form),(Inclusion Criteria: Selected concepts that are descendent of C42636 as determined by the FDA. These concepts are linked to "Structured Product Labeling Pharmaceutical Dosage Form Terminology (Code C54456)" by Concept_In_Subset.),(Exclusion Criteria: Navigational concepts and any concept excluded from the FDA SPL list)
